---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="The SNG Token | Singular">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-8 md:py-16">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">The Singular (SNG) Token</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300">The Core Asset of the Protocol</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-8 bg-gray-900/50 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-lg border border-gray-700">
      
      <!-- Token Details Section -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 border-b border-gray-700 pb-2">Token Details</h2>
        <ul class="list-none space-y-3 mt-4">
          <li class="flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="font-medium text-gray-400">Token Name:</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-white">Singular (SNG)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="font-medium text-gray-400">Standard:</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-white">BEP-20 (Binance Smart Chain)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="font-medium text-gray-400">Total Supply:</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-white">1.00000000 SNG</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="font-medium text-gray-400">Decimals:</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-white">8</span>
          </li>
           <li class="flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="font-medium text-gray-400">Smallest Unit:</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-white">0.00000001 SNG</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Core Principle Section -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 border-b border-gray-700 pb-2">Core Principle: Absolute Scarcity</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
          The total supply of SNG is fixed and immutable. No new SNG fractions can ever be minted after the initial deployment. This absolute scarcity ensures that the value of each fraction is preserved and directly tied to the performance and growth of the DAO's investment portfolio. Your ownership will never be diluted by inflation.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Distribution Section -->
       <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 border-b border-gray-700 pb-2">Distribution</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
          The token distribution is designed for long-term health and community alignment. The allocation ensures the DAO is well-capitalized for its investment mission, while also providing liquidity and rewarding the team. You can review the full distribution table, vesting schedules, and lockup details in our official whitepaper.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-6">
            <a href="/singular-whitepaper.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn">View Whitepaper Tokenomics</a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
